job.title: SSSB Punjab Warder, Matron & Technical Asst. Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 847  Vacancy in Punjab
job.body:
Total vacancies:847

Name of the Posts:

  • Warder (Only for Males) - 815
  • Matron (Only for Females) - 32

Description

New Punjab Government Jobs for 12th pass has been published by Punjab Subordinate Service Selection Board for the posts of Warder, Matron & Technical Asst. . If you are searching for a government job in Punjab then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the post of Warder, Matron & Technical Asst. , from 10-05-2021, and till 31-05-2021 upto 5 pm. If you are interested in all these posts and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

Mode of application is Online

  • The application fee for GEN. candidates are only Rs. 1000/-.
  • The application fee for SC/BC/ EWS candidates is only Rs. 250/-.
  • The application fee for Ex-Servicemen & Dependent candidates is only Rs. 200/-.

Educational qualification :

  • To apply for a Warder, Matron & Technical Asst. vacancies in Punjab, your 10+2 with Punjabi must be completed from a recognized Boards

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply for these posts is 10-05-2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these posts is 31-05-2021 up to 5 pm

Age Limit Criteria

  • To apply for these posts, you should be between 18 to 27  years old. 

PSSSB Warder, Matron & Technical Asst. Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Punjab Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is ₹ 10,300-34800/-.

Physical Eligibility:


For Warder Posts:

Physical Measurement Test (PMT)

  • Physical Standards Minimum Height:
  • 5 Feet 7 Inches
  • 5 Feet 4-1/2 Inches in the case of Dogras & Gurkhas.
  • Chest: 33 Unexpanded 31-1/2 Expanded
  • Vision: Normal in both eyes (with or without Spectacles) (must not be color blind)

Physical Efficiency Test (PET):

 For Male Candidates:

  • 100 Meters Run: 15 Seconds (Only one Chance)
  • Shot Put (7.26 Kg) (16 Pound): 5.50 Meters (Three Chance)
  • Rope Climbing: 15 Feet (Three Chance)

For Matron Posts:

Physical Measurement Test (PMT)

Physical Standards Minimum Height:

  • 5 Feet 3 Inches
  • Weight: 50 Kg & Above
  • Vision: Normal in both eyes (with or without Spectacles) (must not be color blind)

Physical Efficiency Test (PET):

For Females Candidates:

  • 100 Meters Run: 18.5 Seconds (Only one Chance)
  • Shot Put (5.443 Kg) (12 Pound): 4.00 Meters (Three Chance)
  • Rope Climbing: 12 Feet (Three Chance)

How to apply for PSSSB Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Warder, Matron & Technical Asst. . Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of PSSSB and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by PSSSB
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
